title: Bug 116564: Hyperlink builder title changes to 'www.actuate.com' instead of 'Hyperlink Options'
OB: When I click on 'OK' and reopen the hyperlink builder, its title changes to 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', but it currently changes to 'www.actuate.com' based on the settings.
SR:
1. Open the hyperlink builder.
2. Click on 'OK' to close the hyperlink builder.
3. Reopen the hyperlink builder.

Expected Result: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
Actual Result: The title of the hyperlink builder changes to 'www.actuate.com'.
